rows.label: bf09270100_0010
rows.name: Shin!

rows.label: bf09270100_0020
rows.name:
Are you alone?
Where's Metsu?

rows.label: bf09270100_0030
rows.name: He went ahead.

rows.label: bf09270100_0040
rows.name: So what are you doing here then?

rows.label: bf09270100_0050
rows.name: I was waiting for you.

rows.label: bf09270100_0060
rows.name:
For us?
You're trying to stop us from following Metsu?

rows.label: bf09270100_0070
rows.name: Well, perhaps...

rows.label: bf09270100_0080
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]?

rows.label: bf09270100_0090
rows.name: I want to see for myself.

rows.label: bf09270100_0100
rows.name: If this world truly has a will of its own

rows.label: bf09270100_0110
rows.name: I want to see whether it chooses you or Metsu.

rows.label: bf09270100_0120
rows.name: Then let us through.

rows.label: bf09270100_0130
rows.name: I can't do that.

rows.label: bf09270100_0140
rows.name: Why not? You can barely even stand right now!

rows.label: bf09270100_0150
rows.name: If we fight now, you will certainly...

rows.label: bf09270100_0160
rows.name: As expected of you, Hikari.

rows.label: bf09270100_0170
rows.name:
...It's a promise.
To fulfill his wish.

rows.label: bf09270100_0180
rows.name: Even if it means your body will be destroyed?

rows.label: bf09270100_0190
rows.name: That's my earnest desire.

rows.label: bf09270100_0200
rows.name: Shin...

rows.label: bf09270100_0210
rows.name:
Looks like we have no choice but to fight,
Boy.

rows.label: bf09270100_0220
rows.name:
I know.
We're going all out, Shin.

rows.label: bf09270100_0230
rows.name:
That's the spirit.
Bring it on, boy!
